data.description: Now Available! Charming home close to downtown Aiken, Hitchcock Woods, neighborhood pool & playground.-recently renovated & painted inside and out, beautiful hardwood floors. Custom baseboards/trim throughout. French doors lead to a large livingroom with custom glass shelves & lighting. Cook's kitchen with modern appliances and original cabinetry with custom Corian countertops. The cozy family room has a gas fireplace w/ original built-ins. French doors invite you into the sunroom that opens to an outside deck overlooking the lush backyard landscape.The primary bedroom comes with 2 closets and a fully updated en-suite. 2 bedrooms share a Jack and Jill remodeled bathroom. Fourth room can be utilized as bedroom or large utility/craft room and has 3 closets for storage & W/D hookups. The basement has a large finished area with a gas fireplace, recreational room, office, and large storage area. Outside you will find a covered patio, mature landscaping w/ sprinkler system, private fenced backyard. Seller will consider Owner financing
